data.description: If you're looking for turn-key, this is the one! Located on a large corner lot, this charming 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home was fully updated in 2022. The interior boasts an open-concept living, kitchen, and dining area complete with a brick fireplace. Walk-in laundry room with interior access just off the kitchen. Oversized windows in the ADDITIONAL family room create beautiful, natural light and will make you feel right at home. This home is complete with a back patio perfect for entertaining or morning coffee, and a fully fenced back yard and storage shed.  Wonderfully landscaped and ready for you to call "home"! This property is a must-see. Call to schedule your showing  today!
